And then what I find cool as well, let's say if I want to share this view with someone

00:28:03.540 --> 00:28:08.939
so that the person can put it in a notebook or something, I can just convert to code to

00:28:08.939 --> 00:28:13.859
like SQL, Pandas, or Polars, and it can just send it to them.

00:28:13.859 --> 00:28:14.859
So yeah.

00:28:14.859 --> 00:28:20.459
So that type of exploration is something that I'm really interested in data science, both

00:28:21.260 --> 00:28:29.020
through notebooks and data exploration in general, in order to enable people to, when

00:28:29.020 --> 00:28:37.020
they use AI, they can also know what they're doing with their data and so on.

